#. Description of the theme
#, gp-priority: high
msgid "New blog theme is fairly developed theme. It supports Gutenberg editor. It has clean looks and smooth presentation ideally suited for personal blog and magazine type blog. It has used all customizer options available in WordPress. New blog theme is totally controlled and accesed from customizer view. It's design as per demo can be totally achieved from customizer option. Custom widget has been avoided so that even the novice user can use this theme. Many premium features have been provided as free features so that all basics and advance features can be utilized. This is complete package for well content website making business. You can preview demo here: \" http://postmagthemes.com/demonewblog/ \""
msgstr "The New Blog theme is a fairly well developed theme. It supports the Gutenberg editor. It has clean looks and a smooth presentation, ideally suited for a personal blog and magazine type blog. It has used all Customiser options available in WordPress. The New Blog theme is totally controlled and accessed from the Customiser view. Its design, as per the demo, can be totally achieved from the Customiser option. The custom widget has been avoided, so that even the novice user can use this theme. Many premium features have been provided as free features, so that all basic and advanced features can be utilised. This is a complete package for good content websites. You can preview the demo here: \" http://postmagthemes.com/demonewblog/ \""

